@API(status=EXPERIMENTAL, since="0.1") public interface TypedParameterizableGenerator<T> extends TypedGenerator<T>, ParameterizableGenerator
Extension of ParameterizableGenerator for generators that only provide one type of values.

    • nullableRandomValue

      T nullableRandomValue(@NotNull @NotNull Object... params)
      Returns a random value of the supported type for the specified parameter sources allowing null values.

      The returned value has a probability of be null except for native types when no NotNull constraint is present. If not null behaves as randomValue().

      Parameters:
      params - The parameter sources to extract the parameters from
      Returns:
      A random nullable value for the specified type.
